Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了嗎 我都等煩了 姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那表情是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是忘記了這張臉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是銀啊 姬妳的老熟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為我被你這樣挑釁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有要求的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還有交涉的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這樣明事理的町長真是太好了啊 蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然想要參加一下祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能把那裡打開一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿著鑰匙對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神要去洞裡？怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面佈滿了『七鄉』的芽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要把妖力傳送進去 讓『七鄉』開花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 如果做了那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就只有讓這傢伙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被最喜歡的哥哥緊緊抱著身體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為這樣就可以得手嗎？ 姬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:18.66,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)}{\pos(480,335)}是時…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名 把蒼帶走…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是妳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『88(FLAK36 88毫米炮)』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不會讓你跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有受傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好弱吶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管多強的武器 終究只是言靈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不用擔心的 蓧塚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是過分的舉動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你會為高興的慶祝再會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會？怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你沒有說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見到過我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 秋名你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 集中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 銀的拳頭的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不打死你 我保留了力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的蠻有意思嘛 蓧塚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助去姬那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付這傢伙我一個人就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄飛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣驚慌到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 又弄髒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然熱衷工作不錯 但這是很重要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念波還真是便利的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附帶的『覺』的力量 連妳的心都可以讀懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在猶豫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用槍對著這個身體 心情滿是猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是害怕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要殺掉朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？誰是你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逞強也沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳必須要用那雙手傷害銀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然是會猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名也在害怕著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是這麼想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那裡別動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說中了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是円神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『八彩』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那亂套的槍法是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『火消』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『雲切』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的覺悟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有夠可靠的呢 町長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『大花火』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是蕭索的煙花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 円神怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剛才那下砸的好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法完全變成妖怪的東西 是打不過我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在說那種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕著變成妖怪 卻用著妖怪的力量保護著城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳做的事情充滿矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了嗎 你那套我不懂的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『矢』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣息消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是過分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是夥伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢 能不能打開那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去可不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄飛大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地神可以做的頂多只是幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右城鎮命運的事情不可出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成怎麼樣的呢 這個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是火災?哪啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是爆炸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是神社的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃華 姬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 秋明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那個世界現在變成怎樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 原來不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是背負著那個使命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連把妖怪送往怎樣的一個場所你都不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你 知道還是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的世界啊 遠遠慘過人類界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一無所有 是被永恆的停滯所支配著的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於給人類添麻煩的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將他們送往那個世界就再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果『七鄉』之花盛開的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個世界就能和這個世界連接上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界和那邊的世界將會融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與曾將我送去的那個世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你們比泉家曾將我送去的那個世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好心當成驢肝肺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被送歸 是因為你根本就沒有期待著和人類共存吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明人類自己就根本就沒有期待著和妖怪共存
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何妖怪卻需要這種期待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本無心攻擊 槍也變得遲鈍了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這樣臉的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困惑嗎 迷茫嗎 還是猶豫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…不是真正的銀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀依然在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在裡面…在這具身體裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到這種地步了還殘留著靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們全部都不出手嗎…對這具身體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊…試著把他打倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要保護城鎮的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓那些櫻花綻放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就試著讓這具身體消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛快至極啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太幼稚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名…給我把它打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要賞花了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八重大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可要被罰的啊 八重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個臭土地神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…不能就這樣空手而歸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚六爺子 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七鄉』正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界被...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先拿下一城了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖力已經送夠了…再也無法阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七鄉』...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七鄉』…在綻放...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬  『七鄉』…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果花綻放 被送歸的妖怪將會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的平衡就會被打亂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的一切都會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍斬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七鄉』...到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七鄉』綻放的話 這個城鎮也就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上代的町長是這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃華 在裡面 京介在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有…如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴 妳有沒有對未來的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:23:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有的是某一天獨立
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且有一家自己的店
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長也許會喜極而泣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店門弄不能沒有特色想弄的時尚一點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.27,0:24:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面氛圍充滿著爵士樂曲的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家店一定很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣室也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣室？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.26,0:24:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.22,0:24:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集各種關於迷惑的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶…不開拉麵店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.66,0:24:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我討厭拉麵
